title: NDZ's congratula
author: Lowtuff
pages:
#- Congratulations from
New Danzilona on the coronation of the great King Friedrich I! May he live long and bring his nation into a golden age!
While only Neondan99 could witness the coronation itself, he spoke to us of its wonders and we were humbled. Long
#- live the King, God save Prussia and may our peoples grand friendship never falter!
#- 